# textdomain: mcl_powder_snow
Powder Snow=가루눈
This is a block of snow thats extra fluffy, this means players can sink in it=이것은 푹신한 눈 블록으로, 플레이어가 그 안으로 빠질 수 있습니다
Powder Snow Bucket=가루눈 양동이
This bucket is filled powder snow=가루눈으로 가득 찬 양동이
Place it to empty the bucket and place powder snow. Obtain by right clicking on a block of powder snow with an empty bucket.=
Places a powder snow block=
